title: Loan Shark (1952 Film-Noir) Starring George Raft | Directed by Seymour Friedman

sources.title: Loan Shark (1952 Film-Noir) Starring George Raft | Directed by Seymour Friedman
sources.description:
Joe Gargan infiltrates a ruthless loan scheme, pretending to be a tough collector while Ann Nelson doubts his shady act. When Lou Donelli’s gang escalates violent threats, Joe’s fists—and a factory brawl—reveal a twist: playing crook might just save the day (or bankrupt the bad guys).


Colorized version: https://youtu.be/8uRd6cTWElM


Director: Seymour Friedman
Writers: Martin Rackin, Eugene Ling
Stars: George Raft, Dorothy Hart, Paul Stewart
Genre: Crime, Drama, Film-Noir, Thriller
Release Date: April 25, 1952 (Philadelphia USA)
